snippet.title: ∀kashicforce - Inundation of Brigades Official Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
∀kashicforce - Inundation of Brigades will be on Steam in March 2019 in English and Japanese!

Wishlist it here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/857460/kashicforce/

Developed by Endless Shirafu and published by Fruitbat Factory, ∀kashicforce is a puzzle-game-like, rhythm-game-like game where you input commands to use moves like in a fighting game. The goal is to crush your opponent to a pulp with an immense amount of blocks. In order to put yourself in a better position, kill your opponent's blocks while they are falling down or send Hindrance blocks into their field.
